      "para_id": "Q000928.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Ninĝirsu , the powerful warrior of Enlil , his master , Ur-Ninĝirsu , ruler of Lagaš , son of Gudea , ruler of Lagaš , the builder of Ninĝirsu's E-ninnu , built his beloved divine audience chamber from fragrant cedarwood ."
    }
  ],
